## 

>(shell sort)

n/2

```php
<?php

function shellSort($array)
{
    $length = count($array);

    for ($gap = $length >> 1; $gap > 0; $gap >>= 1) {
        for ( $i = $gap; $i < count($array); ++$i ) { 
            $tmp = $array[$i];
            for ( $j = $i - $gap; $j >= 0 && $array[$j] > $tmp; $j -= $gap ) { 
                $array[$j+$gap] = $array[$j];
            }   
            $array[$j+$gap] = $tmp;
        }   
    }   

    return $array;
}

```

